text: KIBE (104.9 FM) is a radio station licensed to Broken Bow, Oklahoma, United States. The station is currently owned by Eastern Oklahoma State College. ==History== This station was assigned call sign KIBE on December 17, 2012. ==References== ==External links== *http://www.radio.eosc.edu/ IBE Category:Radio stations established in 2012
title: KIBE (FM)
